### Version

~~~ .xmp.php
Extend::version($id, $v = null);
~~~

Return the `version` property of `about.page` file in the current extension folder or `0.0.0`:

~~~ .php
$test = Extend::version('minify');
~~~

### Info

~~~ .xmp.php
Extend::info($id);
~~~

Return a page object of `about.page` file in the current extension folder:

~~~ .php
$info = Extend::info('minify');
~~~

### Exist

~~~ .xmp.php
Extend::exist($input, $fail = false);
~~~

Return the folder path of current extension folder if exists:

~~~ .php
if ($path = Extend::exist('minify')) {
    // do something with `$path` â€¦
}
~~~

### State

~~~ .xmp.php
Extend::state($id, $key = null, $fail = false);
~~~

Return the stored extension states if any, otherwise, return `$fail`:

~~~ .php
$state = Extend::state('minify');
~~~